				{
					"text": "The doctor reassured him that there was nothing seriously wrong.",
					"contextForm": "reassure somebody that…"
				},
				{
					"text": "She needed to be reassured of his love for her.",
					"contextForm": "be reassured of something"
				},
				{
					"text": "He was constantly reassuring himself that he had acted for the best."
				},
				{
